2:{i:0;i:1770306822;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:378:"<p>Pivot reports now allow sorting across groups using any selected column, not only the row grouping fields. This gives teams more control when ranking results or analyzing distributions across segments.</p>
