is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:376:"<p>If a ticket is moved from Unassigned to a specific user via manual assignment, Spiro now automatically updates the ticket status to Assigned, removing an extra step and keeping queues consistent.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
