(rather than the year), while older entries from previous years continue to display the year. The change is intended to make “what happened today/this week” easier to scan.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
