:1770221141;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:310:"<p>Sales Orders now include a search bar to locate specific items in large orders more quickly, reducing manual scrolling through long lists.</p>
