 In-app, attachments are indicated with a paperclip and can be previewed (for images), opened in a new tab, or downloaded. The update is consistent across desktop and mobile.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
